cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE 

The paper deals with 3D shape representation and reconstruction, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep learning techniques for this purpose suggests that it may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper's focus on improving accuracy and efficiency through network design and optimization suggests that it may also belong to the neural networks (cs.NE) sub-category.
